## üìÅ Project Structure

After initialization:

```
my-project/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ .specpulse/          # SpecPulse configuration
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ .claude/commands/    # Claude Code slash commands
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ .gemini/commands/    # Gemini CLI slash commands
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ memory/              # Project context and decisions
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ context.md       # Current feature, decisions
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ templates/           # Specification templates
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ spec.md
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ plan.md
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ task.md
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ specs/               # Feature specifications (created on-demand)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ plans/               # Implementation plans (created on-demand)
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ tasks/               # Task breakdowns (created on-demand)
```

**Note**: No `scripts/` folder! v2.1.0+ uses pure Python CLI.

**v2.1.3 Additions**:
- `.specpulse/logs/` - Application logs with rotation
- Enhanced config validation
- 27 new sp-* CLI commands
- Metadata tracking in all files
- Context-aware operations

