## üéØ Why SpecPulse?

### Before SpecPulse

```
‚ùå No standardized workflow
‚ùå Specifications often outdated
‚ùå Hard to track feature progress
‚ùå Manual context switching
‚ùå Inconsistent documentation
```

### After SpecPulse

```
‚úÖ Standardized SDD workflow
‚úÖ Specifications always up-to-date
‚úÖ Automatic progress tracking
‚úÖ Smart context detection
‚úÖ Consistent, validated documentation
```

